<p class="lead">Start thinking. Ask questions to get your group thinking.</p>

<ul>
  <li>How would your group respond if a stranger were weeping under the table? How should you respond?</li>
  <li>Jesus is worthy of our passion and commitment. How does your life reflect this hunger and thirst for Jesus? How could it reflect that passion more?</li>
  <li>Since â€œJesus is bigger than politics,â€ how does your conversation during the week reflect this truth?</li>
