<p class="lead">Start sharing. Choose questions that create openness.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Is your own circle too small to include the lost and hurting? Who are people in your circle who need Jesus?</li>
  <li>Since we are living letters (2 Corinthians 3:2), what version of Jesus do people see when they read your life?</li>
  <li>How has shame kept you from growing relationships? What about from pursuing Jesus?</li>
  <li>We all are broken. What brokenness has Godâ€™s amazing grace saved you from?</li>
  <li>How has your past given you the grace to love others?</li>
  <li>What desperation in your life leads you to worship? How will you pursue worship this week?</li>
</ul>

